    "body": "### Fixed\n\n- **`login_anthropic()` ‚ÄĒ token exchange body ŪėēžčĚ JSON Ž≥ĶÍ∑Ä + `anthropic-beta`\n  Ūó§ŽćĒ ž†úÍĪį.** v0.99.2 ÍįÄ `application/x-www-form-urlencoded` Ž°ú Ž≥ÄÍ≤ĹŪēėÍ≥†\n  `anthropic-beta: oauth-2025-04-20` Ž•ľ ž∂ĒÍįÄŪĖąžúľŽāė žā¨žö©žěź žčúŽŹĄ Í≤įÍ≥ľ žó¨ž†ĄŪěą\n  `invalid_request`. ../openclaw + ../claude-code Í∑łŽĚľžöīŽĒ© + Claude Code\n  native binary žĚė `h6.post(TOKEN_URL, z, {headers:{\"Content-Type\":\n  \"application/json\"}, timeout:30000})` Ūėłž∂ú žěźž≤īŽ•ľ ž∂Ēž∂úŪēėžó¨ ground truth\n  ŪôēžĚł:  Content-Type žĚÄ JSON, beta Ūó§ŽćĒŽäĒ token endpoint žóź Ž≥īŽāīžßÄ žēäžĚĆ.\n  v0.99.0/0.99.1 žĚė JSON ŪĆ®ŪĄī žěźž≤īŽäĒ ŽßěžēėžúľŽāė host (`api.anthropic.com`)\n  ÍįÄ ŪčÄŽ†łŽćė Í≤É ‚ÄĒ v0.99.2 ÍįÄ host fix žôÄ Ūē®ÍĽė Content-Type ÍĻĆžßÄ žĚėžč¨ŪēīžĄú\n  žěėŽ™ĽŽźú Žį©ŪĖ•žúľŽ°ú ŽįĒÍĺľ žÖą. Í≥ĶžčĚ docs / community gist žĚė \"form-urlencoded\"\n  ž†ēŽ≥īÍįÄ ž†ēŪôēŪēėžßÄ žēäŽč§ŽäĒ Í≤įŽ°†.\n\n- **`login_anthropic()` ‚ÄĒ reverted token exchange body to JSON + dropped\n  `anthropic-beta` header.** Even after the v0.99.2 host fix the user\n  still saw `invalid_request`. Grounding against the openclaw + claude-code\n  source trees plus extracting the actual `h6.post` call site from\n  claude.exe (`{\"Content-Type\":\"application/json\"}`, no beta header)\n  confirmed the binary is the ground truth: JSON-only on the token\n  endpoint, no anthropic-beta. Public docs and community gists are\n  incorrect on this point."
