    "body": "### Fixed\n\n- **`login_anthropic()` ‚ÄĒ token endpoint host + Content-Type + timeout ž†ēž†ē.**\n  v0.99.1 manual-paste fix ŪõĄžóźŽŹĄ `/login anthropic` ÍįÄ `invalid_request`\n  Ž°ú ÍĪįž†ą. žā¨žö©žěź žĹėžÜĒ žč†Ūėł + Claude Code native binary žĚė prod env ÍįĚž≤ī\n  `K3q` ž†Ąž≤ī ž∂Ēž∂ú + Í≥ĶžčĚ Ž¨łžĄú cross-check Ž°ú 3 ÍįÄžßÄ root cause Ūôēž†ē:\n  ‚Ď† token endpoint host ÍįÄ `https://platform.claude.com/v1/oauth/token`\n  (`api.anthropic.com` žĚÄ inference API ž†Ąžö©); ‚Ď° Content-Type žĚÄ\n  `application/x-www-form-urlencoded` ŽßĆ Ūóąžö© ‚ÄĒ `application/json` žúľŽ°ú\n  Ž≥īŽāīŽ©ī žĚĎŽčĶ žßÄžóį/timeout ÍįÄŽä•; ‚ĎĘ žĚĎŽčĶ žčúÍįĄ 40-60s Ž≥īÍ≥†ÍįÄ žěąžĖī client\n  timeout žĚĄ 15s ‚Üí 60s Ž°ú žôĄŪôĒ. `_ANTHROPIC_TOKEN_URL` ž†ēž†ē + `json=` ‚Üí\n  `data=` body ŪėēžčĚ Ž≥ÄÍ≤Ĺ + httpx timeout 60s.\n\n- **`login_anthropic()` ‚ÄĒ corrected token endpoint host, Content-Type, and\n  timeout.** Post-v0.99.1 the manual-paste flow still failed with\n  `invalid_request`. Three root causes pinned down via the prod env object\n  `K3q` extracted from Claude Code's native binary plus cross-check with\n  official docs: ‚Ď† OAuth audience lives on\n  `platform.claude.com/v1/oauth/token` (`api.anthropic.com` only serves\n  the inference API); ‚Ď° endpoint accepts only\n  `application/x-www-form-urlencoded` ‚ÄĒ `application/json` causes hang/\n  timeout; ‚ĎĘ reported 40-60s response time under load, so client timeout\n  relaxed from 15s to 60s. Fixed `_ANTHROPIC_TOKEN_URL`, switched httpx\n  body from `json=` to `data=`, set Timeout(60)."
