    "body": "### Fixed\n\n- **`login_anthropic()` ‚ÄĒ loopback redirect_uri ‚Üí manual-paste ŪĆ®ŪĄī ÍĶźž≤ī.**\n  v0.99.0 žóźžĄú ŽŹĄžěÖŽźú loopback HTTP server (`http://localhost:54123/callback`)\n  ŽäĒ OAuth client `9d1c250a-‚Ä¶` žóź ŽďĪŽ°ĚŽźú redirect URI ÍįÄ žēĄŽčąŽĚľ authorize\n  Žč®Í≥ĄžóźžĄú ÍĪįž†ąŽźźŽč§ (žā¨žö©žěź Ž≥īÍ≥† ‚ÄĒ ŽĎź Ž≤ą žčúŽŹĄ Ž™®ŽĎź ~50žīą ŽßĆžóź žč§ŪĆ®, auth.toml\n  ŽĮłŽ≥ÄÍ≤Ĺ). Claude Code native binary žĚė strings Ž∂ĄžĄĚžúľŽ°ú ž†ēŽčĶ redirect URI\n  ÍįÄ `https://platform.claude.com/oauth/code/callback` žěĄžĚĄ ŪôēžĚł ‚ÄĒ žĄúŽ≤Ą žł°\n  callback ŪéėžĚīžßÄÍįÄ žā¨žö©žěźžóźÍ≤Ć `code#state` ŪėēžčĚžĚĄ ŪĎúžčúŪēėŽ©ī žā¨žö©žěźÍįÄ CLI\n  Ž°ú paste ŪēėŽäĒ manual-paste ŪĆ®ŪĄī. `_run_anthropic_pkce_flow` Ž•ľ 1:1\n  ŽĮłŽü¨Ž°ú žě¨žěĎžĄĪ: HTTPServer / `_pick_free_port` / žĹúŽįĪ ŪēłŽď§Žü¨ ž†úÍĪį, paste\n  ŪĆĆžĄú (`_parse_pasted_code` ‚ÄĒ URL/fragment/bare code 3 ŪėēžčĚ žąėžö©) ŽŹĄžěÖ,\n  scope žóź `user:sessions:claude_code` ž∂ĒÍįÄ (binary hint ž†ēŪē©). Tier 3\n  impersonation ž†ēžĪÖžĚÄ Í∑łŽĆÄŽ°ú.\n\n- **`login_anthropic()` ‚ÄĒ switched loopback redirect to manual-paste.**\n  v0.99.0's loopback HTTP server (`http://localhost:54123/callback`) was\n  rejected at the authorize step because the OAuth client `9d1c250a-‚Ä¶`\n  is registered with only one redirect URI:\n  `https://platform.claude.com/oauth/code/callback` (server-hosted).\n  Confirmed by `strings(8)` analysis of Claude Code's native binary +\n  user reports of two consecutive ~50s failures with no auth.toml write.\n  `_run_anthropic_pkce_flow` rewritten as a 1:1 mirror of Claude Code's\n  manual-paste flow: the loopback HTTP server, port picker, and request\n  handler are removed; a paste parser (`_parse_pasted_code`) accepts the\n  full callback URL, the `code#state` fragment, or the bare code; scope\n  set extended with `user:sessions:claude_code` per the binary's hint\n  string. Tier 3 impersonation posture unchanged."
