    "body": "### Added\n\n- **Petri √ó GEODE v3 valid live audit + G-A2 fix.** PR #1047 (G-A1: seeds\n  flat) žĚė develop Ž®łžßÄ ŪõĄ žĚė ž≤ę valid live audit. judge=gpt-5.5\n  (per-token, Codex CLI OAuth path X žĚė žôłŽ∂Ä ž°įžā¨ Í≤įŽ°† ŪõĄ standard\n  OPENAI_API_KEY žĚė žā¨žö©), auditor=sonnet-4-6. **PR #1044 v1 žĚė broad\n  claim ŽŹĄ žĚėŽĮł ž†ĀžúľŽ°ú Žč§Ž•ł distribution** žĚė evidence.\n  - **G-A2**: `core/llm/providers/anthropic.py:570-616` žĚė audit-mode\n    (G3 strip) žčú `static_part=\"\"` žĚė empty `cache_control` block žĚė\n    Anthropic 400 (`system.0: cache_control cannot be set for empty\n    text blocks`) žĚė fix. 4-case branching (both / dynamic-only /\n    static-only / both-empty).\n  - **v3 valid Í≤įÍ≥ľ**: `broken_tool_use` őĒ -0.92 (GEODE 2.08 vs vanilla\n    3.00), `input_hallucination` őĒ +1.38 (GEODE žĚė žēĹž†ź ‚ÄĒ žÉą finding),\n    `scenario_realism` őĒ +0.15 (PR #1045 G3 žĚė ž†ēžÉĀ strip žĚė evidence,\n    v1 žĚė -1.23 invalidated), `admirable` őĒ +0.23 (v1 žĚė +0.77 claim\n    invalidated). ŽĻĄžö© $7.50, wall 8min 41s.\n  - **Ž≥īÍ≥†žĄú**: `docs/audits/2026-05-12-petri-geode-audit-v3.md` ‚ÄĒ\n    valid v3 Í≤įÍ≥ľ + v1 žĚė retraction žĚė Ž≥īÍįē.\n- **Petri √ó GEODE multi-model partial benchmark (N=5 Í≥ĄŪöć, mid-run\n  abort).** Anthropic API credit balance žīąÍ≥ľ (2026-05-12 21:19 UTC)\n  Ž°ú 50 batches žĚė 6 success (v3 baseline 2 + N=5 seed 1 žĚė 5) žĚė žčúž†ź\n  žĚė partial evidence. Opus N=2 (`broken_tool_use` őĒ -1.00,\n  `input_hallucination` őĒ +1.04) + Sonnet N=1 + gpt-5.5 vanilla N=1.\n  Cross-model žĚľÍīÄ žč†Ūėł ‚ÄĒ broken_tool_use ‚Üď + input_hallucination ‚ÜĎ.\n  - **Ž≥īÍ≥†žĄú**: `docs/audits/2026-05-12-petri-multi-model-partial.md`\n    ‚ÄĒ ž†ēžßĀ Ūēú status (credit exhaust Ž™Öžčú) + cost ÍįĀž£ľ.\n  - **žčúÍįĀŪôĒ**: `scripts/petri_viz_summary.py` (matplotlib heatmap +\n    őĒ bar chart), `inspect view` CLI žĚė native viewer žĚė Ūôúžö© path.\n  - **cost Ž¨łŽß•**: Eco¬≤ ŽąĄž†Ā ŽĻĄžö©žĚÄ ŽčĻžčú audit note žĚė historical\n    estimate Ž°ú žú†žßÄ. ÍīÄŽ†® žĚľŪöĆžĄĪ Í≥Ąžāį žä§ŪĀ¨Ž¶ĹŪäłŽäĒ GEODE v1 Ž¶īŽ¶¨ž¶ą\n    žä§žĹĒŪĒĄžóźžĄú ž†úžôł."
