    "version": "0.88.5",
    "date": "2026-05-09",
    "body": "> **Hardening ‚ÄĒ `core/graph.py` `# type: ignore[call-overload]` 9 ÍĪī ž†úÍĪį\n> (B2 batch-3).**  9 Íįú langgraph `add_node()` Ūėłž∂úžĚė ignore Ž™®ŽĎź ž†úÍĪį.\n> žõźžĚł: žöįŽ¶¨ `_node()` wrapper žĚė ŽįėŪôė ŪÉÄžěÖ `Callable[[GeodeState], dict[str, Any]]`\n> žĚī langgraph žĚė `_Node[NodeInputT_contra]` Protocol Í≥ľ mypy žěÖžě•žóźžĄú\n> žěźŽŹô Žß§žĻ≠ŽźėžßÄ žēäžĚĆ (mypy ÍįÄ generic Callable žĚĄ Protocol member Ž°ú\n> žěźŽŹô coerce ŪēėžßÄ žēäžĚĆ).  Solution: ``_node`` žĚė ŽįėŪôėžĚĄ langgraph žĚė\n> ``_Node[GeodeState]`` Protocol Ž°ú Ž™Öžčú + ŽįėŪôėÍįížĚĄ `cast()` Ž°ú localise.\n> 9 Íįú ignore ‚Üí 0, mypy ÍįÄ `add_node` overload Ž•ľ ÍĻ®ŽĀóžĚī resolve.\n\n### Changed\n- **`core/graph.py:_node`** ‚ÄĒ return ŪÉÄžěÖ `Callable[[GeodeState], dict[str, Any]]` ‚Üí `_Node[GeodeState]` (langgraph internal Protocol).  ŽāīŽ∂ÄžóźžĄú `cast(_Node[GeodeState], _make_hooked_node(...))` / `cast(_Node[GeodeState], fn)` Ž°ú wrapped/raw fn Ž™®ŽĎź Protocol Ž°ú localise.  Runtime ŽŹôžěĎ Ž≥ÄŪôĒ 0 (langgraph ŽäĒ dict-shape return žĚĄ Í∑łŽĆÄŽ°ú ŽįõžĚĆ).\n- **9 Íįú `add_node` Ūėłž∂ú (line 514‚Äď522)** ‚ÄĒ `# type: ignore[call-overload]` ž†úÍĪį.  `router`, `signals`, `analyst`, `evaluator`, `scoring`, `skip_check`, `verification`, `synthesizer`, `gather` 9 ŽÖłŽďú Ž™®ŽĎź.\n\n### Hardening Metrics\n- `# type: ignore` žīĚŪē©: 53 ‚Üí **44** (active count, ‚ąí9, ‚ąí17 %)\n- `[call-overload]` žĻīŪÖĆÍ≥†Ž¶¨: 13 ‚Üí 4 (graph.py 9 ‚Üí 0; tracing/tools/pipeline_executor 4 žěĒž°ī ‚ÄĒ root-cause Žč§Ž•ł SDK ŪēúÍ≥Ą)\n- pytest 4346 passed (Ž≥ÄŽŹô žóÜžĚĆ); ruff/mypy clean (332 source files); E2E A (68.4) ŽŹôžĚľ."
