    "body": "### Added\n- **HookSystem audit (42 ‚Üí 46 events)** ‚ÄĒ 4 lifecycle event ž∂ĒÍįÄ (SHUTDOWN_STARTED, CONFIG_RELOADED, MCP_SERVER_CONNECTED/FAILED) + 12 table-driven audit logger + S4 ŽĻĄŽĆÄžĻ≠ žąėž†ē (memory_tools hook ŽįúŪôĒ) + 3 trigger site ž∂ĒÍįÄ"
