    "body": "Plan/Sub-agent NL integration, Claude Code-style UI, response quality hardening.\n\n### Added\n\n#### Plan & Sub-agent NL Integration\n- `create_plan` tool ‚ÄĒ NLŽ°ú Ž∂ĄžĄĚ Í≥ĄŪöć žÉĚžĄĪ (\"Berserk Ž∂ĄžĄĚ Í≥ĄŪöć žĄłžõĆž§ė\")\n- `approve_plan` tool ‚ÄĒ Í≥ĄŪöć žäĻžĚł ŽįŹ žč§ŪĖČ (\"Í≥ĄŪöć žäĻžĚłŪēī\")\n- `delegate_task` tool ‚ÄĒ žĄúŽłĆžóźžĚīž†ĄŪäł Ž≥ĎŽ†¨ žúĄžěĄ (\"Ž≥ĎŽ†¨Ž°ú ž≤ėŽ¶¨Ūēī\")\n- NL Router tool count: 17 ‚Üí 20 (plan/delegate 3Íįú ž∂ĒÍįÄ)\n- Offline fallback: plan/delegate regex ŪĆ®ŪĄī ž∂ĒÍįÄ (LLM žóÜžĚī ŽŹôžěĎ)\n\n#### Claude Code-style UI\n- `core/ui/agentic_ui.py` ‚ÄĒ tool call/result/error/token/plan Ž†ĆŽćĒŽü¨\n- `core/ui/console.py` ‚ÄĒ Rich Console žčĪÍłÄŪÜ§ (width=120, GEODE ŪÖĆŽßą)\n- Marker system: `‚Ėł` tool call, `‚úď` success, `‚úó` error, `‚úĘ` tokens, `‚óŹ` plan\n\n#### LangSmith Trace Coverage\n- `@_maybe_traceable` added to verification layer: `run_guardrails`, `run_biasbuster`, `run_cross_llm_check`, `check_rights_risk`\n- Full pipeline tracing coverage: router ‚Üí signals ‚Üí analysts ‚Üí evaluators ‚Üí scoring ‚Üí verification ‚Üí synthesizer\n\n### Changed\n- `AgenticLoop._process_tool_calls()`: `str(result)` ‚Üí `json.dumps(result, ensure_ascii=False, default=str)` ‚ÄĒ LLMžĚī ŪĆĆžčĪ ÍįÄŽä•Ūēú JSON ŪėēžčĚžúľŽ°ú tool Í≤įÍ≥ľ ž†ĄŽč¨\n- `snapshot._persist_snapshot()`: `json.dumps(..., default=str)` ‚ÄĒ non-serializable ŪēĄŽďú žēąž†Ą ž≤ėŽ¶¨\n- `snapshot.capture()`: `_sanitize_state()` ž∂ĒÍįÄ ‚ÄĒ `_`-prefixed ŽāīŽ∂Ä ŪēĄŽďú ŪēĄŪĄįŽßĀ\n- NL Router offline fallback žąúžĄú: plan/delegate ŪĆ®ŪĄīžĚĄ known IP Žß§žĻ≠Ž≥īŽč§ Ž®ľž†Ä Í≤Äžā¨\n\n### Fixed\n- Offline mode `_run_offline()`: action name(\"list\") ‚Üí tool name(\"list_ips\") Žß§ŪēĎ ŽąĄŽĚĹ žąėž†ē (`_ACTION_TO_TOOL` dict ž∂ĒÍįÄ)\n- `_TOOL_ACTION_MAP` ŽąĄŽĚĹ: `create_plan`, `approve_plan`, `delegate_task` ŽĮłŽďĪŽ°Ě ‚Üí ž∂ĒÍįÄ\n\n### Infrastructure\n- Test count: 1909+ ‚Üí 2000+\n- Module count: 116 ‚Üí 118\n- `tests/test_agentic_ui.py` (20 tests), plan/delegate NL tests (20 tests)"
